title: WOW Wrestling, Bad Bumbles & Leaving Neverland (w/ Eleanor Kerrigan & Joe DeRosa)
description: Eleanor Kerrigan joins the show and talks about the Philly Mob and WOW Wrestling. After watching the trailer for “Leaving Neverland” Jay and Dan say who could have gotten to them. Joe DeRosa joins Dan and Jay on board the Impractical Jokers cruise for a discussion of Teen Wolf.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
